    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                
                <salute>Dear H<ptr target="tex.00447_n1"/>&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>This comes here, by absurd fault of address<ptr target="tex.00447_n2"/>&#8212;So I
                forward it to you&#8212;all goes on about the same with me<ptr target="tex.00447_n3"
                />&#8212;I have rec'd a handsome present of horse &#38; light wagon<ptr
                    target="tex.00447_n4"/>&#8212;was down to Glendale<ptr target="tex.00447_n5"/> all day last Sunday&#8212;all
                well&#8212;Ruth home, with <hi rend="italic">her baby</hi>, Harry home&#8212;trouble with throat&#8212;Mr
                and Mrs Stafford well&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Love to you and your dear mother&#8212;</salute>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p>Sept 22</p>
